	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Author:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>thefox</b> [ Fri Jul 19, 2013 9:02 pm ]</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: New in Nes development</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Shiru, the first line of your bat file doesn't work correctly:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">path=path;..\bin\</div><br />This will set the path to, literally, &quot;path;..\bin\&quot;. It should be:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">path=%path%;..\bin\</div><br />This is unrelated to any CC65 problems.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


